{{Infobox book | name = The Encyclopedia of Serbian Historiography | title_orig = Енциклопедија српске историографије | author = Sima Ćirković, [[Rade Mihaljčić]] | country = [[Serbia]] | language = [[Serbian language|Serbian]] | subject = [[Serbian history]] | publisher = Knowledge | pub_date = 1997 | media_type = Print ([[Hardcover]]) | pages = XVI, 741 | isbn = 86-80269-35-2 | congress= DR1961 .E53 1997 | oclc= 38020597 }} '''''The Encyclopedia of Serbian Historiography''''' is a one-volume encyclopedia on [[Serbia]]n [[historiography]] and related historical sciences ([[art history]], [[literary history]], [[ethnology]] and [[archaeology]]), edited by [[Sima Ćirković]] and [[Rade Mihaljčić]].
== Structure ==
The encyclopedia features articles by more than 350 authors. It is divided into three parts:
