{{Infobox Museum | name = Florida Municipal Museum | native_name = Museo Municipal de Florida | native_name_lang = Spanish
| map_type = Cuba | map_caption = <small>Location of museum in [[Florida, Cuba|Florida]]</small> | coordinates = {{coord|21.525645|-78.223976|display=inline}} | established = {{Start date|1981|12|12|df=y}} | location = Carretera Central No. 501 e/ República y Libertad, [[Florida, Cuba|Florida]], [[Camagüey]], [[Cuba]] | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} '''Florida Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in [[Florida, Cuba|Florida]], [[Cuba]]. It was established on 12 December 1981.<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/566 Museo Municipal de Florida]</ref> The museum holds collections on history, weaponry, archeology, [[numismatics]], and natural science.
